{"tid":622354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"崔天凱：美國應調整老大自居心態　中方願將蛋糕做大　否則只會到手的蛋糕就都可能沒有","createTime":"2018-04-09T05:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T11:16:33.000Z","uid":188,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"84410710d71c03f971747c81cca91b88c7ce45a9","tid":622354,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"中國駐美大使崔天凱再度評論中美的貿易戰，他表示，美國一些人應該調整習慣以世界老大自居的心態，建立開放共贏的世界觀，世界上的事情要大家共同商量，不能一家說了算，一家說了也不可能算。 崔天凱接受內地傳媒訪問時重申，中方一貫主張，任何問題都應該通過對話磋商來解決，由於國情的差異，雙方對很多問題的看法不可能完全一致，矛盾和分歧始終存在。崔天凱表示，中美的分歧是在於切蛋糕的大小上，他認為，這個問題其實可以商量，如果雙方一起將蛋糕做大，那麼大家都能切到更大的一塊，如果打貿易戰，到手的蛋糕就都可能沒有。 <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1390142-20180409.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1390142-20180409.htm&d=pKbYicPFoXxHwxGNo8RD4v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a8c8dc85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1390142-20180409.htm&h=8ebd039f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1390142-20180409.htm</a></span>"},{"pid":"d2ce7588f41eb1fad65f5e0c4aece1f6163f6e1c","tid":622354,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40c490c580a1750602477c6c53759b2f99a16e3","tid":622354,"uid":35430,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"大陸造嘅蛋糕你自己吔飽佢啦<br />\n有冇睇chilam廣告呀"},{"pid":"7b763fe48e624e926cedb323acdaa5e4309cbac6","tid":622354,"uid":188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"呢到幾時輪到你話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfc63de8d64dde91e2a5bb3aa2